The '''Corphelion Comets''' was a celestial phenomenon over [[Corphelion]]. The silver light and movement from the [[Comet/Legends|comets]]' display were a popular tourist attraction and mood setter for romantic getaways.

As the comets were a natural phenomenon instead of being created by intelligent beings, they were not included in the list of the [[Twenty Wonders of the Galaxy]] by the historian [[Vicendi]] in in his [[10,000 BBY]] publication ''[[Arturum Galactinum]]''.<ref name="EA">''[[The Essential Atlas]]''</ref>

[[Han Solo/Legends|Han]] and [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Solo]] stopped on Corphelion to see the light show in the early stages of their honeymoon.

